spec_data.Name: perl-Apache-Session-Browseable
spec_data.Description:
A virtual Apache::Session back-end providing some class methods to manipulate
all sessions and add the capability to index some fields to make re-search
faster.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 03 Oct 2017 11:19:00 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Add index and search methods to Apache::Session
